<h3 class="date"><a href="/2012/jun/20/">&#x27a0;</a> June 20, 2012</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="satellite-eyes" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://satelliteeyes.tomtaylor.co.uk/">Satellite Eyes</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Fab tiny OS X app which sets your desktop wallpaper to a satellite view of your current location. Added bonus: You can switch to use the gorgeous &#8220;Watercolour&#8221; themed maps by Stamen.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
