<h3 class="date"><a href="/2010/jul/21/">&#x27a0;</a> July 21, 2010</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="flipboard-ipad" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.flipboard.com/">Flipboard for iPad</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Beautiful social news gathering tool for iPad. Feeds are &#8220;curated&#8221; using Twitter lists, giving buttloads of flexibility. (Sadly the social part is buggered at the moment, as they didn&#8217;t account for all the iPad users out there)</p>

<p>Unrelated: New goal in life: Create a product that is cool, then get Adam Lisagor to make the promo video.</p>

