<h3 class="date"><a href="/2009/nov/29/">&#x27a0;</a> November 29, 2009</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="waze" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.waze.com/homepage/">Waze</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Free car routing app for iPhone, which is using game mechanics (points &amp; leaderboards) to crowd-source maps and traffic info.  Initial prodding suggests it&#8217;s not ready for prime-time &#8212; you&#8217;re better off waiting for protonerds to fill up their data banks &#8212; but it might be worth watching in the future.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
